OL,3,CBoy, 11, seriously injured after a hit
OL,4,Cand run in Birmingham
OL,6,FAn 11-year-old boy has been left with
OL,7,Fserious head injuries after being hit
OL,8,Fby a van in the Hodge Hill area of
OL,9,FBirmingham.
OL,11,FWest Midlands Police has launched an
OL,12,Finvestigation after the boy was struck
OL,13,Fby a silver Vauxhall Vivaro moments
OL,14,Fafter he got off a bus near the Clock
OL,15,FGarage on Coleshill road on Saturday
OL,16,F31 August, shortly before 6:40pm.
OL,18,FThe boy was rushed to hospital where
OL,19,Fhe underwent surgery. He remains at
OL,20,Fthe hospital in a stable condition.
