OL,4,Cand run in Birmingham
OL,6,FThe driver of the van failed to stop.
OL,7,FSince the collision, the vehicle has
OL,8,Fbeen seized but police are now
OL,9,Fappealing for witnesses or anybody
OL,10,Fwith information to help them identify
OL,11,Fthe driver.
OL,13,FDetective Sergeant Paul Hughes, from
OL,14,Four Serious Collision Investigation
OL,15,FUnit, said: "The boy suffered a
OL,16,Fsignificant head injury and we need to
OL,17,Ftalk to the driver.
